Prehistoric Oral tradition, cave art ~10^9 (brain) Face‑to‑face Tribal cohesion
Agricultural Writing (clay, papyrus) 10^{10}–10^{12} Scribes, messengers Bureaucracy, law
Classical Libraries, roads 10^{13}–10^{14} Couriers, ships Empires
